<title>CZECH REPUBLIC: Czech cbank says Q1 C/A deficit $1.069 bln.</title>
<headline>Czech cbank says Q1 C/A deficit $1.069 bln.</headline>
<dateline>PRAGUE 1997-06-06</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Czech Republic's current account deficit for the first quarter of the year totalled $1.069 billion while its capital account was in surplus by $782.4 million, the central bank (CNB) said on Friday.</p>
<p>				     Q1 97	     FY 1996</p>
<p> CURRENT ACCOUNT ($ mln)   -1,069.2	   -4,475.8</p>
